      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? Use two pans!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
