            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>tamari soy sauce </strong>and <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>to a measuring jug with your <strong>cornflour</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[70ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[90ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong></p>",
