          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash, then, slice your <strong>pak choi </strong>into wedges lengthways on a clean chopping board and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
