    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the <strong>hoisin sauce </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is coated – this is your <strong>sticky hoisin chicken</strong></p>",
